== 訴訟案 ==

=== ZeniMax Media訴Mojang AB ===

[[贝塞斯达软件公司|贝塞斯达软件公司]]的母公司[[ZeniMax_Media|ZeniMax Media]]於2011年9月27日起訴Mojang計劃將其開發的遊戲Scrolls註冊商標，侵犯了貝塞斯達開發的遊戲系列[[上古卷轴系列|上古卷軸]]（The Elder Scrolls）的版權。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/113339-Mojang-and-Bethesda-Are-Going-to-Court|title=Mojang and Bethesda Are Going to Court|work=Escapist Magazine|date=2011-09-27|accessdate=2011-09-29|author=Chalk, Andy|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111021114624/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/113339-Mojang-and-Bethesda-Are-Going-to-Court|archive-date=2011-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>於10月18日，馬庫斯·佩爾松公佈Mojang勝出訴訟案，但貝塞斯達仍能提出上訴。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://pc.ign.com/articles/120/1200949p1.html | last = Goldfarb | first = Andrew | title = Notch Wins First Round Against Bethesda | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2011-10-27 | accessdate = 2011-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111020204711/http://pc.ign.com/articles/120/1200949p1.html | archive-date = 2011-10-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>於2012年3月，Mojang與贝塞斯达達成和解，Mojang決定放棄為Scrolls註冊商標，但贝塞斯达亦不能阻止Mojang使用「Scrolls」作為遊戲名稱。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/165441/Bethesda_Mojang_settle_Scrolls_trademark_lawsuit.php | last = Graft | first = Kris | title = Bethesda, Mojang settle 'Scrolls' trademark lawsuit | work = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2012-03-11 | access-date = 2013-08-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160721144331/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/165441/Bethesda_Mojang_settle_Scrolls_trademark_lawsuit.php | archive-date = 2016-07-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>在此期間，佩爾松開玩笑地邀請貝塞斯達與他進行一場《[[雷神之锤III竞技场|雷神之锤III竞技场]]》遊戲來解決糾紛。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://notch.tumblr.com/post/9038258448/hey-bethesda-lets-settle-this|title = Hey, Bethesda! Let’s settle this!|date = 2011-08-17|accessdate = 2013-07-25|website = The World of Notch|first = Markus|last = Persson|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130820202141/http://notch.tumblr.com/post/9038258448/hey-bethesda-lets-settle-this|archive-date = 2013-08-20|dead-url = no}}</ref>

=== Uniloc美國訴Mojang AB ===

於2012年7月20日，[[Uniloc|Uniloc]]起訴Mojang，指出《我的世界攜帶版》侵犯了Uniloc在Android設備上檢查許可證的專利權。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://notch.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/mojang.pdf |last=Bumgardner |first=Barry |title=Uniloc USA, Inc. et. al. v. Electronic Arts Inc. |publisher=United States District Court for the Eastern District of Texas - Tyler Division |date=2012-07-20 |accessdate=2012-07-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120721135821/http://notch.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/mojang.pdf |archivedate=2012-07-21 }}</ref>之後，Uniloc收到大量投訴郵件。因此，Uniloc創辦人里克·理查森發表聲明，指起訴Mojang並不是他的決定。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/118649-Uniloc-Creator-Denies-Mojang-Lawsuit-Involvement | last = Chalk | first = Andy | title = Uniloc Creator Denies Mojang Lawsuit Involvement | publisher = ''[[The_Escapist_(magazine)|The Escapist]]'' | date = 2012-07-23 | accessdate = 2012-07-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130518111854/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/118649-Uniloc-Creator-Denies-Mojang-Lawsuit-Involvement | archive-date = 2013-05-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

